                  </hi> I live in Fetter-lane. On the 24th of June, about one o'clock, I saw the prisoner go into Mr. Charles' shop, and come out with some coats on his arm—I am sure there was more than one coat.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> I was not taken till a month afterwards; what do you swear to me by? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> By your face—I knew you by sight for a couple of months, by passing along Ship-yard.</p>
